@startuml
autonumber
skinparam maxMessageSize 150
skinparam ParticipantPadding 20
skinparam BoxPadding 10

actor "ÖİDB Staff" as Staff

box "Presentation Layer" #LightCyan
participant "ui : OidbDashboardUI" as UI
end box

box "Business Logic Layer" #LightYellow
participant "verifController : DocumentVerificationController" as VerifController
participant "routeController : RoutingService" as RouteController
end box

box "Data Access Layer" #LightGreen
participant "appRecord : TransferApplication" as AppDB
participant "docRecord : BaseDocument" as DocDB
end box

== 1. Accessing the Review Page ==
Staff -> UI: Navigate to OİDB Dashboard
activate UI

UI -> UI: filterByStatus("Pending Verification")
note right: Filters the view to only show incoming applications

UI -> VerifController: fetch pending applications list
activate VerifController
VerifController -> AppDB: Query TransferApplications (status="Pending")
activate AppDB
AppDB --> VerifController: Return list of applications
deactivate AppDB
VerifController --> UI: Application list data
deactivate VerifController

UI --> Staff: displayPendingApplications()

== 2. Document Verification Process ==
Staff -> UI: Select specific student's application to review
UI -> VerifController: verifyDocuments(applicationId)
activate VerifController

VerifController -> AppDB: Fetch TransferApplication details
activate AppDB
AppDB --> VerifController: Application details
deactivate AppDB

VerifController -> DocDB: Fetch associated documents (Transcript, YKS, etc.)
activate DocDB
DocDB --> VerifController: Document files
deactivate DocDB

VerifController --> UI: Render application data and document viewer
deactivate VerifController

alt Invalid or Missing Documents (Alternative Flow)
    Staff -> UI: Flag document as invalid/missing & submit note
    UI -> VerifController: requestDocumentCorrection(applicationId)
    activate VerifController

    VerifController -> AppDB: setStatus("Correction Requested")
    activate AppDB
    AppDB --> VerifController: Status updated
    deactivate AppDB

    VerifController --> UI: Correction logged successfully
    deactivate VerifController
    
    UI --> Staff: showActionConfirmation() ("Student notified for correction")

else Documents are Valid (Normal Flow)
    Staff -> UI: Approve all documents
    UI -> VerifController: Mark application as verified
    activate VerifController
    
    VerifController -> DocDB: lockDocument()
    note right: isLocked is set to true to prevent further student uploads
    activate DocDB
    DocDB --> VerifController: Documents locked
    deactivate DocDB
    
    VerifController --> UI: Verification complete
    deactivate VerifController

    == 3. Application Routing ==
    Staff -> UI: Proceed to routing decision
    
    alt Needs English Proficiency Prep (YDYO)
        UI -> RouteController: forwardToYDYO(applicationId)
        activate RouteController
        RouteController -> AppDB: setStatus("Forwarded to YDYO")
        activate AppDB
        AppDB --> RouteController: Status updated
        deactivate AppDB
        RouteController --> UI: Routing complete
        deactivate RouteController
        UI --> Staff: showActionConfirmation() ("Routed to YDYO")
        
        
    else Reject Application (e.g., General constraints not met)
        UI -> RouteController: rejectApplication(applicationId)
        activate RouteController
        RouteController -> AppDB: setStatus("Rejected")
        activate AppDB
        AppDB --> RouteController: Status updated
        deactivate AppDB
        RouteController --> UI: Rejection complete
        deactivate RouteController
        UI --> Staff: showActionConfirmation() ("Application Rejected")
    end
end

deactivate UI
@enduml